message.text:
Get to know JPMAP-FEU! ✨

The Junior People Management Association of the Philippines – FEU is more than just an organization — it’s a training ground for future leaders who value teamwork, integrity, and growth. Here, you’ll discover what people management truly means and how it can prepare you for both your academic and professional journey. 🌿

Be part of our community and start your journey with us! Apply now through this link:
👉 https://forms.office.com/r/2vJGHzsGP2
👉 https://forms.office.com/r/2vJGHzsGP2
👉 https://forms.office.com/r/2vJGHzsGP2

May be a graphic of map and text that says "Whatis is JDMAR The Junior People Management Association of the Philippines- FEU (JPMAP-FEU) is a student organization that helps members become future leaders by teaching them the basics of people management, or simply, how to work well with others and guide them toward shared goals. In almost every career, you will need to know how to work with, guide, and manage people -whether it's in small team, a department, or an entire company. People management is about understanding others, building good relationships. and helping people stay motivated and productive. FB/X:@JPMAPFEU IG:@JPMAP_FEU EMAIL:JPMAP@FEU.EDU.PH"

May be a graphic of slow loris and text that says "Mission JPMAP-FEU FEU focuses on preparing members to become effectivef future People Managers. It does this by: 1 camaraderie among members. FB/X:@JPMAPFEU IG:@JPMAP_FEU @JPMAP EMAIL:JPMAPPFEU.EDU.PH"

May be a graphic of text that says "Vision JPMAP-FEU envisions itself as a recognized university- wideorganization under JPMAP and PMAP that: it empowers and develops its members, guiding them from being students into well-prepared professionals. It aims to shape them into future leaders and People Managers who will not only succeed in their careers but also make meaningful contributions to society. In essence, the vision emphasizes the long-term goal of transforming students into socially responsible individuals and professionals who can lead with competence, integrity, and purpose. In almost every career, you will need to know how to work with, guide, and manage people -whether it's in small team, a department, or an entire company. message.text:
Get to know JPMAP-FEU! ✨

The Junior People Management Association of the Philippines – FEU is more than just an organization — it’s a training ground for future leaders who value teamwork, integrity, and growth. Here, you’ll discover what people management truly means and how it can prepare you for both your academic and professional journey. 🌿

Be part of our community and start your journey with us! Apply now through this link:
👉 https://forms.office.com/r/2vJGHzsGP2
👉 https://forms.office.com/r/2vJGHzsGP2

message.text:
Ang IABF Student Council ay higit pa sa isang samahan—ito ay buklod ng pagkakaisa, paglilingkod, at kahusayan. 🏛️❤️

Sa likod ng bawat inisyatibo ay ang mga dibisyon ng konseho—bawat isa ay may mahalagang papel sa paghubog ng karanasan ng bawat estudyante. Mula sa paglikha ng mga oportunidad, pagtitibay ng koneksyon, at pangangalaga sa kapakanan ng estudyante, sabay-sabay silang kumikilos para sa iisang layunin: ang maglingkod.

Narito ang mga dibisyong nagsisilbing haligi ng Konseho—bawat isa may sariling misyon at dedikasyon upang panatilihing buhay ang ating paglilingkod. 

#FinestKwentoEveryKanto 
#SoaringGreaterHeights

Pubmat by Alyanna Madrideo, Yesha Eugenio, Gellie Causapin

Ang IABF Student Council ay higit pa sa isang samahan—ito ay buklod ng pagkakaisa, paglilingkod, at kahusayan. 🏛️❤️

Sa likod ng bawat inisyatibo ay ang mga dibisyon ng konseho—bawat isa ay may mahalagang papel sa paghubog ng karanasan ng bawat estudyante. Mula sa paglikha ng mga oportunidad, pagtitibay ng koneksyon, at pangangalaga sa kapakanan ng estudyante, sabay-sabay silang kumikilos para sa iisang layunin: ang maglingkod.

Narito ang mga dibisyong nagsisilbing haligi ng Konseho—bawat isa may sariling misyon at dedikasyon upang panatilihing buhay ang ating paglilingkod. 

#FinestKwentoEveryKanto

message.text:
Ang IABF Student Council ay higit pa sa isang samahan—ito ay buklod ng pagkakaisa, paglilingkod, at kahusayan. 🏛️❤️

Sa likod ng bawat inisyatibo ay ang mga dibisyon ng konseho—bawat isa ay may mahalagang papel sa paghubog ng karanasan ng bawat estudyante. Mula sa paglikha ng mga oportunidad, pagtitibay ng koneksyon, at pangangalaga sa kapakanan ng estudyante, sabay-sabay silang kumikilos para sa iisang layunin: ang maglingkod.

Narito ang mga dibisyong nagsisilbing haligi ng Konseho—bawat isa may sariling misyon at dedikasyon upang panatilihing buhay ang ating paglilingkod. 

#FinestKwentoEveryKanto 
#SoaringGreaterHeights

Pubmat by Alyanna Madrideo, Yesha Eugenio, Gellie Causapin
